er ask him for to do a combine for a high price item even with parts without offering him pp for the combine.  It's cool to ask friends for combines and see if you can get it done by a guildee, but to expect them to do it or be upset if they want a donation is rather greedy.  trade skills are pricey to max and it's only fair to offer donation for something you can't do yourself even if you do have the parts.<br>
